      • isGroundTypeValid

        public byte isGroundTypeValid()
        Returns if the ground is a valid block type for this plant to be grown on. If the item is not on the ground 0 will bre returned.
        Returns:
        0 if item is not on the ground. If the block is valid returns 1 otherwise -1 if the block type is invalid.

      • plant

        public boolean plant()
        Attempts to place the plant. If the plant has not been ticked long enough for it to be planted then it will return false and not be placed.
        Returns:
        true if the plant was placed.
